Privacy Policy
At Rocket-Skin-Lab, we are committed to protecting your personal data. This privacy policy explains what information we collect, how we use it, and what measures we take to keep it secure. We are dedicated to complying with applicable laws, including the General Data Protection Regulation (GDPR).

1. Data Collected
We collect the following data when you interact with our site:

Personal information (name, email address)
Connection information (IP address, browser type)
Purchase-related information (order history)

2. Use of Data
The data we collect is used for the following purposes:

To provide and improve our services
To manage your orders and payments
To ensure site security and prevent fraud

3. Data Sharing
Your data is only shared with trusted third parties necessary for service operation:

Payment providers for example we use Stripe, payments are not handled by ourselves.
Data hosting and storage providers. We do not share your information for advertising purposes without your consent.


5. Data Retention
We retain your personal data only for as long as necessary to provide our services or comply with legal obligations.

6. Your Rights
Under the GDPR, you have the following rights regarding your personal data:

Right of access: You can request access to the personal data we hold about you.
Right of rectification: You can request correction of any inaccurate or incomplete information.
Right of deletion: You can request the deletion of your personal data.
Right to object and withdraw consent: You can object to the processing of your data or withdraw your consent at any time.
To exercise your rights, please contact us at: rocketskinlab@gmail.com.

7. Data Security
We implement appropriate technical and organizational measures to safeguard your personal data, including encryption and firewalls.

8. Policy Changes
This privacy policy may be updated. We will notify you of any significant changes by posting the new version on our website.

9. Contact
If you have any questions regarding this privacy policy or your personal data, you can contact us at: rocketskinlab@gmail.com.